description:
Add this Ai Ai icon next to your username! This icon features Ai Ai from Super Monkey Ball.

Icons are pictures that display next to your Amigo's username during gameplay.

This icon is included in the Super Monkey Ball Costume & Accessories Pack.
Purchasing the Super Monkey Ball Costume & Accessories Pack will make this icon available for your Amigo in the shop menu.
name: Ai Ai Icon
